# рџ“‚ PDF & DOCX to Markdown Converter

A simple Python script that converts all **PDF** and **DOCX** files inside a folder into clean **Markdown (.md)** files.

Built using **Docling**.

---

## рџљЂ Why This Project?

When building:

* RAG systems
* AI chatbots
* Q&A assistants
* Knowledge base search systems

You first need clean, structured text.

PDF files are layout-based and messy.
Markdown is clean and structured.

This script automates:

```
Folder with PDFs/DOCX в†’ Clean Markdown files
```

Perfect for the data ingestion phase of AI pipelines.

---

## рџ“¦ Features

вњ… Converts all `.pdf` and `.docx` files
вњ… Skips unsupported file types
вњ… Creates output folder automatically
вњ… Keeps original filenames
вњ… Handles errors per file
вњ… Simple and beginner-friendly

---

## рџ›  Requirements

